  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You inspire dread in other foes when you slay an enemy.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Intimidating Prowess, Intimidate 4 ranks, slayer level 4th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you reduce your target to below 0 hit points with a melee attack, as a swift action you can attempt an Intimidate check to demoralize all foes within 30 feet who can see your attack.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you confirm a critical hit, you can spend 5 stamina points and take a swift action to attempt an Intimidate check to demoralize all foes within 30 feet who can see your attack.",
